{"tid":2338543,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"之前律政司用排期揀法官，現在不用了，有國安法制度，明目張膽指派","createTime":"2020-12-24T05:44:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-24T05:48:54.000Z","uid":261647,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"40cd576947328ed984b2fc03aaceb87e68791e2c","tid":2338543,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T05:44:14.000Z","msg":"https://twitter. com/LungZenoOpen/status/1335241135946493953<br />\n<br />\n之前律政司用排期挑選法官，現在不用了，有國安法法官制度，就這樣明目張膽指派用國安法法官。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2663098520592889\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flynnleiwong%2Fposts%2F2663098520592889&d=otIFGLHjmDp%2FicXUVK76MbQTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=314fbe7d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2663098520592889</a><br />\n<br />\n以胸襲警案嘅時候連魚蛋都未發生。用排期出術揀法官，更加係一早就有。屈襲警，用假口供定罪，食過翻尋味，然後不斷做不斷升級，跟住就係魚蛋。<br />\n<br />\n司法根本係問題嘅另一環，甚至係主導，所以從來都唔係險。唔係險走去守即係自尋死路，叫人去守就更加仆街。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2760095220893218\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flynnleiwong%2Fposts%2F2760095220893218&d=otIFGLHjmDp%2FicXUVK76MbQTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=17a54d9c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2760095220893218</a><br />\n<br />\n中國：我要揀法官。<br />\n李國能：唔得架，咁樣影響司法獨立。應該加個步驟，由張舉能推薦，咁樣先至冇口實！<br />\nCIA哈佛法學院fresh grad：呢條友弱智架???<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2600577356845006\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flynnleiwong%2Fposts%2F2600577356845006&d=otIFGLHjmDp%2FicXUVK76MbQTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=1d917b38\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2600577356845006</a><br />\n<br />\n用排期出術，我講過無數次，口水都乾。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2366964246872986\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flynnleiwong%2Fposts%2F2366964246872986&d=otIFGLHjmDp%2FicXUVK76MbQTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=5de95821\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2366964246872986</a><br />\n<br />\n香港政府係點樣喺mag仔揀合作嘅官呢？好簡單，合作嘅裁判官會定時定候坐Court 1，就專登喺嗰日提堂。合作嘅官會好合作咁排期比自己審，然後繼續合作。近年越來越嚴重。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2366966706872740\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flynnleiwong%2Fposts%2F2366966706872740&d=otIFGLHjmDp%2FicXUVK76MbQTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=e0ae6a3a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2366966706872740</a><br />\n<br />\n依家唔止mag仔可以揀法官，例如「反佔中反黑警司」吳偉漢案，個官有track record。於是第一單暫委上去地院就係大家合作，ICAC疑似有heart嘅朋友查完，檢控鳩做，認罪超短刑期，真係開心。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2366960050206739\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flynnleiwong%2Fposts%2F2366960050206739&d=otIFGLHjmDp%2FicXUVK76MbQTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=bc4578b1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2366960050206739</a><br />\n<br />\n講起引渡，好好奇卡利斯坦獨立戰士文子星引渡案嘅東區裁判官係邊個，係咪又係老招數計準當值時間揀個超級公正法官。 司法守尾門喎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"985f18ab1b00617e5dbbe124b6a00c52297ee119","tid":2338543,"uid":325118,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T05:48:54.000Z","msg":"司法獨立 OMDB.jpg <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}